Package: webdav
Type: Package
Title: A Simple Interface for Interacting with WebDAV Servers
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
            person("Andre", "Leite", email = "leite@castlab.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
            person("Hugo", "Vaconcelos", email = "hugo.vasconcelos@ufpe.br", role = "aut"))
Description: This package provides an easy-to-use interface for interacting with WebDAV servers,
    including OwnCloud. It simplifies the use of WebDAV methods such as COPY, LOCK, MKCOL, MOVE,
    PROPFIND, and others. With built-in authentication and request handling, it allows for easy
    management of files and directories over the WebDAV protocol.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: 
    httr2 (>= 0.2.0),
    glue (>= 1.4.2)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    roxygen2
URL: https://github.com/yourusername/webdav
BugReports: https://github.com/yourusername/webdav/issues
